---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Mark Wild Portfolio";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <div class="text-slate-800">
    <p class="text-5xl bold pb-10 font-roboto">Mark Wild</p>
    <div class="text-2xl pb-10">
      <p class="pb-10">
        Hey! I'm Mark, and I’ve spent 5 years in the aerospace industry, helping

        <a
          href="https://astra.com/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-blue-500 hover:underline"
          >launch rockets and manufacture satellite engines<span
            class="text-slate-800">.</span
          >
        </a> I currently work to support the next generation of manufacturing robotics
        at
        <a
          href="https://www.agilityrobotics.com/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-blue-500 hover:underline"
          >Agility <span class="text-slate-800">.</span>
        </a>

        I specialize in IT infrastructure and operations. I like to solve
        technical problems by building teams, bridging technology, and
        delivering impactful results. I am interested in education, <a
          href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Third_place"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-blue-500 hover:underline"
          >third spaces<span class="text-slate-800">,</span>
        </a> literature, and the environment.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can also find me on
        <a
          href="https://github.com/MorkWood2"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">GitHub</a
        >
        and
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mark-wild/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">LinkedIn</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
